ass=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-question-circle\"></i>Where is the dog park in Monroe, NC?</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-question-circle\"></i>Are there hiking trails near Monroe?</button></div></div><div role=\"list\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-accordion\"><article role=\"listitem\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-row \"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-main\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-index\">01</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><h4 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Where is the dog park in Monroe, NC?</h4><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-preview\">Sunset Park features a designated dog park area, making it a convenient spot for off-leash play within the city limits.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-meta\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-chip\">Facilities &amp; Features</span><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></div></button><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-answer\"><p style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.7\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Sunset Park features a designated dog park area, making it a convenient spot for off-leash play within the city limits.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel-actions\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Category · <!-- -->Facilities &amp; Features</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a panel-buttons\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-hand-thumbs-up\"></i> Helpful</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-share\"></i> Share</button></div></div></div></article><article role=\"listitem\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-row \"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-main\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-index\">02</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><h4 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Are there hiking trails near Monroe?</h4><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-preview\">Yes, nearby Cane Creek Park provides excellent hiking trails around a large lake.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-meta\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-chip\">Planning Your Visit</span><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></div></button><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-answer\"><p style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.7\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Yes, nearby Cane Creek Park provides excellent hiking trails around a large lake. It’s a great spot for a day trip with your dog.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel-actions\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Category · <!-- -->Planning Your Visit</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a panel-buttons\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-hand-thumbs-up\"></i> Helpful</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-share\"></i> Share</button></div></div></div></article><article role=\"listitem\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-row \"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-main\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-index\">03</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><h4 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">What is the leash law in Monroe?</h4><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-preview\">Monroe requires dogs to be on a leash and under control when off the owner’s property.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-meta\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-chip\">legal</span><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></div></button><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-answer\"><p style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.7\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Monroe requires dogs to be on a leash and under control when off the owner’s property. This is strictly enforced in public parks.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel-actions\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Category · <!-- -->legal</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a panel-buttons\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-hand-thumbs-up\"></i> Helpful</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-share\"></i> Share</button></div></div></div></article><article role=\"listitem\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-row \"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-main\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-index\">04</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><h4 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Is downtown Monroe pet-friendly?</h4><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-preview\">The revitalized downtown area is becoming more pet-friendly, with walkable sidewalks and occasional events that welcome leashed dogs.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-meta\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-chip\">socializing</span><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></div></button><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-answer\"><p style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.7\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">The revitalized downtown area is becoming more pet-friendly, with walkable sidewalks and occasional events that welcome leashed dogs.</p></div><div cla